(3223, 5, 1, 5, '2015-02-10', 'Five Stars love it'),
(3224, 6, 1, 3, '2015-11-28', 'Good little toaster! Toast does not brown evenly. Bottom half gets brown - then you have to turn it around so other half browns. If they can remedy this - it is a very nice economic toaster. The fact that crumb tray pulls out to empty is a very convenient and cleaner way to empty crumb tray.'),
(3225, 6, 1, 4, '2014-05-25', 'Nice Toaster I really like the \'push up\' on this toaster.  When your toast is done, it pops up, but you can push the control up farther up to get the hot toast out.'),
(3226, 8, 1, 5, '2016-02-27', 'Great So far I\'m loving this. Working great with no issues.'),
