(4031, 3, 1, 3, '2015-06-23', 'The controls are not easily managed, otherwise works did not come with detailed instruction manual. The manual provided is skimpy to say the least. The controls are not easily managed, otherwise works fine'),
(4032, 2, 1, 1, '2016-08-06', 'Built to obsolescence! We ordered this toaster oven on March 16, 2016 and over the weekend it stopped working (July 31, 2016).  I would NOT recommend it. Had to go out to Sam\'s and buy a new toaster!  Ugh!.'),
