(4839, 10, 1, 5, '2015-11-18', 'Five Stars very good'),
(4840, 10, 1, 5, '2015-08-06', 'Five Stars Perfect. I will recommend for everyone.'),
(4841, 5, 1, 5, '2015-03-03', 'Perfect Coffee Maker for me! Brews a great cup of coffee. Extremely easy to operate.'),
(4842, 5, 1, 5, '2016-02-16', 'Better than the last 2 coffee pots we had Easy to fill and clean.'),
(4843, 5, 1, 5, '2015-07-30', 'Amazing! This coffee pot is simply amazing and easy to use! With some coffee makers you have to go through so many setting and options to program it but with this coffee maker it\'s simple. I love the option to remove the back to fill it up with water instead of  just the carafe. It does not come with a reusable basket filter but that\'s just fine because coffee filters are super cheap.'),
(4844, 5, 1, 4, '2015-02-23', 'Good coffee. Works great, good tasting coffee on the bold setting. Can\'t ask for more for the price, would recommend.'),
