(4866, 5, 1, 5, '2015-07-18', 'I\'m really gland to have this in our pantry because of some features like the digital temperature indicator and the 12 cups capa as a big fan of brewed coffee, I\'m really gland to have this in our pantry because of some features like the digital temperature indicator and the 12 cups capacity which makes it more power-saving and convenient machine! a must have for all coffee enthusiasts!'),
