(4868, 11, 1, 2, '2014-01-14', 'Tiny and flimsy I order this one because my current B&D has served its life; when I got it, I was shock to see how small and flimsy this one is, comparing to my current 4 slices B&D. I sacrifice the S&H and return it to Amazon.'),
