(5258, 2, 1, 2, '2016-07-07', 'which is quite annoying. I wouldn\'t purchase it again with toast in ... Though it performs most of the functions of a toaster well, including bake, the timer for shades of toast doesn\'t work. We always have to watch over the toast to make sure it doesn\'t burn, which is quite annoying. I wouldn\'t purchase it again with toast in mind.'),
