(5262, 5, 1, 5, '2015-05-06', 'Five Stars I really like this coffee maker.  It makes great coffee and takes up minimal counter space.'),
(5263, 5, 1, 1, '2016-10-10', 'Bad quality. Bad quality...  Have had for a couple of months and already problems.  First, my older Mr Coffee made better coffee.  This maker you need about 20% more coffee to make a good cup - this makes weak coffee.  Second, it offers a \"brew option\" - regular, 1-4 cups and bold.  This option stopped working.  Also the front panel that surrounds the clock and all the push buttons falls off when you open the door where the coffee filter basket is.  I will limp along with it until the coffee maker dies (which sounds like it is on it\' way).'),
