(5294, 4, 1, 1, '2015-03-09', 'smack If I could give this product a 0, I would.  I used this toaster oven 5 times to toast bread. Tried to toast bread today and it will not work in any plug. I think it burned up because it had a burning smell to it.  Save your money.  This one is no better than the cheap ones.'),
(5295, 12, 1, 4, '2014-11-15', 'It looks great in my kitchen. Great little toaster oven that doesn\'t take up too much space. It\'s small so it heats up food in the oven very fast. Only reason I didn\'t give it 5 stars is because my bagel got stuck in the pop-up toaster part, it was easy to pull out.'),
