(5648, 2, 1, 1, '2015-05-19', 'have owned 3 other Black & Decker Toaster ovens in ... have owned 3 other Black & Decker Toaster ovens in the past.  This is by far the cheapest made model Plus  too small for us to use for \'warm ups\' - as we had with our past toaster/ovens.  not impressed - returned the next day.  However, very impressed with the return policy.  worked smoothly and refund received within a few days'),
(5649, 7, 3, 3, '2016-07-20', 'Works good...time will tell just how good. Replaced with this after number three of another expensive very well known named brand stopped working (only had to pay for one). The only things I find wrong with this coffee maker are the little platform that you use for a smaller cup looks as though it could fall easily and to fill with water and coffee you have to move it from under the cabinet as the lid won\'t open up far enough (very inconvenient).'),
(5650, 6, 1, 5, '2015-01-23', 'Don\'t do this at home Best replacement for the toaster I burned up by trying to reflect the heat back in with a cookie tray. I was trying to get the old toaster to toast more evenly.'),
(5651, 10, 1, 3, '2015-05-03', 'This is a good blender. However This is a good blender.  However, it is not great with ice cubes - it is simply not powerful enough.  It is better if you freeze your ingredients (fruit, etc.) or use crushed ice/small cubes.'),
