(5661, 12, 1, 4, '2016-04-28', '... counter toaster ovens for years but have been very disappointed in the last one We always had the under the counter toaster ovens for years but have been very disappointed in the last one. Reviews for this product were promising and so far we like the way it works. My only complaint is I think it looks a little cheesy appearance wise. Paint is so so and came chipped.'),
(5662, 8, 1, 3, '2016-09-15', 'Three Stars for us was great because dont have much space but is small.'),
(5663, 2, 1, 1, '2015-10-22', 'Burns Grilled Cheese This toaster does not cook evenly if you are trying to toast a sandwich or make a grilled cheese. This is due to there being only one level for you to put the rack. If you like to toast your bread one slice at a time, then this isn\'t a problem. If you like to put a sandwich/grilled cheese in the oven and have a burnt top and uncooked bottom, then you\'d probably like this toaster oven. If I could go back in time I would not have purchased this specific toaster oven.'),
(5664, 10, 1, 4, '2015-07-27', 'Four Stars This is great for personal smoothies but I wish it was a little bit stronger.'),
(5665, 4, 1, 4, '2016-09-23', 'Fits The Bill This is a wonderful little toaster oven. And it\'s lightweight enough for us to store  in a lower cabinet and move to the countertop for use. ( like keeping countertops clear).  The toast comes out uniform top and bottom. Controls could be easier to read but  I am sure they will become more familiar with use.'),
(5666, 2, 1, 1, '2016-05-26', 'which makes it pretty difficult because the shelf is 1 The toaster that arrived in the box is not the toaster pictured on the cover of the box or the picture.  The picture shows a toaster oven with two slots to slide in the toasting grid.  This one only has one.  The manual says not to put anything in the toaster oven within 1.5 inches from the heating element, which makes it pretty difficult because the shelf is 1.75 inches from the shelf.  The picture shows the shelf on the lower of the two slots ... which would make it easier to use.'),
(5667, 6, 1, 5, '2015-11-06', 'good toaster I had this toaster and am still pleased with it. This one was purchased as a gift. I recommend it.'),
(5668, 10, 1, 1, '2015-05-06', 'Blades sounded like they were stuck when pulsed Not sure if I just received a defective blender, but I tried making a smoothie and this blender did not do the job. I added frozen fruit and yogurt. Blades sounded like they were stuck when pulsed.  I attempted to add less frozen fruit-nothing changed. Very disappointing.'),
(5669, 10, 1, 4, '2016-02-03', 'Four Stars it\'s a great product. But you can only blend soft stuffs.'),
(5670, 2, 1, 1, '2015-12-20', 'Should not be a #1 best seller I have no idea why this toaster is a #1 best seller. My wife and I hate it. My mother-in-law has one, too, and she hates it. We primarily use it as a toaster, but the dial you use to set how light or dark you want your toast is impossible adjust consistently. The dial doesn\'t click when you turn it, so you never really know where you are in the spectrum between light and dark. The slightest turn too far to the right and your toast is burnt, and the slightest turn to the left and it\'s hardly toasted at all. The solution is to sit there an watch it. Even then, it doesn\'t toast evenly.'),
(5671, 4, 1, 5, '2016-01-21', 'Five Stars Beautiful appliance. Works very well'),
(5672, 3, 1, 5, '2015-07-04', 'This item is very good and works like a dream This item is very good and works like a dream. So glad I bought it but all your item are top of the line. Always very satisfied you. Don\'t down grade.'),
