(6179, 2, 1, 1, '2016-10-19', 'Really awful toaster This might work as a tiny oven, but it is the pits as a toaster.  I throw away a lot of toast and bagels since I bought this. It either barely heats it or burns it black because you can\'t adjust the timer precisely. You have to stand right by it the whole time to watch it or you will have a smoking burnt piece of bread. As a bonus the unit doesn\'t turn off when you open the door.'),
(6180, 5, 1, 5, '2014-10-12', 'I LOVE this coffee maker I LOVE this coffee maker. The removable water reservoir is so nice easy to refill and measure. Love the swing out coffee basket. Coffee STAY hot while on the burner. easy to program. so glad I purchased.'),
