(6193, 5, 1, 5, '2014-08-18', 'Perfect Price Tag Perfect price tag, thing brews great coffee. What more can I ask for?!'),
(6194, 1, 1, 4, '2015-08-17', 'Many improvements in the 2.0 I\'ve used three different models and love the variety of cup size and brew that the 2.0 offers. Also, the compact shape is a big improvement. We live in an older house and the first few models would not fit under our kitchen cabinets. Many complain that the generic pods don\'t work in these, but there are hacks out there for that. We bought the one w/o the carafe and don\'t ever plan on using that. Overall, we love the 2.0. Thanks,Keurig, for the free pods for this review.'),
