(6775, 12, 1, 5, '2016-09-28', 'Surprise! Great little toaster - only wish I had sooner! I was on the fence buying this funky hybrid toaster, but thought for the price was with a shot. Often a good idea in theory doesn\'t work out well as an actual product... Not the case with the Toastation. I\'ve been completely satisfied with this toaster with over a month of regular usage. I needed to replace a traditional toaster over which was being used 80% for toasting, 20% for reheating/baking. My only gripe was that there appeared to be many different model numbers for this toaster on amazon, and I found it a bit confusing which to get.  There are 2 models, an old and a new, and the colors black, and red have separate model numbers. I was also debating between the older model (this one), or the newer one, whose main appeal was a larger (taller) oven area.  Many people dislike the newer one because: it made loud beeping noises, the tray no longer comes out when opening the door, and is made of a lower quality of material, and no longer has the nice retro look.  I was concerned the oven space might be too small on the older model, but in fact its been just fine. Pros: Looks great small size footprint Toasts well, fast, and adjustable settings Easy to clean - crumb collection tray (newer model does not have) Opening door, tray comes forward (newer model does not) Has a cancel feature  pops the toast up. Size of toasting slots fine.  many complain about not being large enough for bagels. Toasted maybe 10 bagels, and only once did it get stuck coming up. nbd. Cons: None Toaster is good for 1-2 people. There is larger version of this toaster that has 2 slots for toasting bread (model 24708) available on Hamilton Beach website, but oddly not amazon.'),
(6776, 6, 1, 5, '2015-08-13', 'This is a wonderful toaster! It toasts beautifully This is a wonderful toaster!  It toasts beautifully, you can set the toasting level easily, and you can even press the cancel button and it releases the handle and pops your bread right back up if you changed your mind about your toasting level.  It is wide enough to fit bagels, too.  Will buy again and again if I ever need a new one.'),
