(6803, 10, 1, 5, '2015-06-04', 'I\'m very nervous about it burning out but so far so good. I dont hold the button down for any ... I\'ve been using this to make smoothies from frozen fruit and it has held up so far. It is very simple to operate and the motor has sufficient strength. It does let out a slight burning smell if you keep it on too long. I\'m very nervous about it burning out but so far so good. I dont hold the button down for any longer than 15 seconds at a time.'),
(6804, 4, 1, 1, '2015-02-03', 'Warning, avoid this product. This product lasted only 6 months.'),
(6805, 4, 1, 1, '2015-01-22', 'Toaster worked great, fit well with small counter space Bought this in July 2014. for a toaster oven. Toaster worked great, fit well with small counter space.  After ~3 months the door hinge started to stick a bit when opened. After 6 months it is not possible to open. Going back I see this complaint on a few other reviews and would definitely not buy this again. It leaves me with questions about the company though I\'ve had many of their products since the 70s.'),
