(6807, 6, 1, 5, '2014-10-13', 'Better than I hoped for I wanted a basic two-slice toaster.  It just had to toast, not cook a five-course dinner.  This is perfect.  The sensor is very, well, sensitive and I can get just the degree of toastedness I want.  The defrost feature works very well. And it has a feature I had never seen.  It has a lift bar so small items can be raised to a height where they can be reached without burning your fingers or unplugging and using a fork to extract. The design is sleek and modern, almost streamlined.  The front has no distracting labels so it looks nice on the counter.  This is so much better than my last toaster--highly recommended.'),
