(6813, 7, 3, 5, '2015-07-01', 'So far it is working great, just one note make sure the basket arm for kcups is in place properly before putting in or it will get jammed in place and it may not come out without forcing it. Lucky it didnt break. If you forget to push the front lever down all you get is hot water. Dont over fill with water, always fill the cup you will be using with water and put that into machine each time before making a cup or you may have it over flow. Had that happen one time. The machine will hold more than one 8oz cup of water. But other than that excellent very flexible brewing machine because it takes 3 types of coffee so you are not a slave to one and can use what ever you can afford at the moment. Slim design does not take up a lot of counter space. Great value for thre price!'),
