(7365, 6, 1, 3, '2017-01-11', 'It will do Working out OK.  However don\'t think it is weighted properly or equally.  When you push the handle down to toast, the rear of the unit flips up.  Have to hold it down, so that\'s what we do.  Also the degree of crispness for the toast-- haven\'t yet worked out what setting to ensure that.  So far seems to brown the outside of the bread, but not crisp up the interior for a good crunch.'),
