(7372, 7, 3, 4, '2014-02-16', 'Got this item despite all the negative reviews. Glad to own this item now. Read a lot about the leaking around the maker, and this is true if I am not careful when putting water in the system. It only holds 8oz and the holding basin is very small, so when you pour water into it fast, Yes it spills out some. My daughter said \"Dad it leaks around the cup platform.\" I informed her that yes it does because she is pouring the water in slow and when she puts the cup on the platform to brew, the water around the outside of the cup makes it appear that there is a leak. SO this leaking problem is owner error. So yes 4 stars......would be five 5 if the basin was bigger and or wider to help pour water in. Thanks HB a great item to own.'),
