(7376, 6, 1, 5, '2014-01-03', 'Cuisinart toaster. This was a gift to a young woman going off to college. The feedback from her and her family when visiting were all 5 star. It was a really nice gift and the joy that it provided was far in excess of its cost which was very reasonable. Here one spends a little more and gets a lot in return. Great value.'),
(7377, 12, 1, 5, '2016-05-06', 'It\'s great because now people can heat up stuff like leftover ... I ordered this for our office break room.  I was just going to get a regular toaster because I wanted to be able to toast my bagels in the morning and then I came across this little gem.  You can use it as a toaster or an oven just by sliding a little bar.  It\'s great because now people can heat up stuff like leftover pizza (which just doesn\'t taste the same if you heat it up in a microwave) or toast a bagel.  I am really glad I found this, and everyone at the office loves it. This is my own opinion of the product and yours may vary. I received no monetary compensation and I am not required to give a good review. If you look at all my reviews, you will see I do not always leave 5 stars and will point out flaws in a product. If my review was helpful to you, would you please vote yes. I provide honest feedback with the pros and cons I can see in a product as well as facts that a potential customer might find useful.'),
(7378, 1, 1, 4, '2015-06-30', 'Works well! This is the first Keurig I have personally owned (having used friends\' previously)  and I really like it! It preheats quickly, and does all that I need in a brewer. My only issue with it is that you must wait while it preheats before you can start the brewing cycle. Aside from that, I really enjoy the machine. Thanks, Keurig, for the free pods for this review.'),
(7379, 2, 1, 1, '2015-06-09', 'Do not get this, get something different It takes ages to toast couple of breads, forget about baking. I would have returned this, but opened the package little late than the allowed return policy time frame. I do not give 1 star to products that often, but this was exceptionally bad purchase. I should have paid little more and got a better one.'),
(7380, 9, 1, 5, '2016-08-08', 'DCC-3000 best bang for the buck. Great coffee maker works very well didn\'t find any issues with the coffee gage. Great product you need to read the manuel and set up the unite correctly if you don\'t follow all the instructions you will have less than a satisfactory experience.'),
