(7382, 5, 1, 5, '2016-05-12', 'Very good coffee maker that does everything I want. This coffee maker does everything I want it to do.  This is my third coffee maker of this particular model.  It\'s easy to setup for the next morning.  It has three temperature settings to keep the coffee warm and I choose the lowest setting to prevent the coffee from tasting burned in case I don\'t drink it quick enough.'),
