(7390, 9, 1, 3, '2015-08-18', 'Over flow valve stops functioning @ 4 months I initially loved this coffee pot, however, I have only had it 4 months and it is already broken.  The lever is stuck open so the coffee just pours out onto the counter.  I tried to return it but their return policy has expired now.'),
(7391, 2, 1, 1, '2015-01-27', 'SHOCK ALERT - I almost died. Ok, not really, but it hurt really bad. SHOCK ALERT!  It\'s not like I was taking a bath with a toaster on the side, trying to toast a bagel or something...I was simply in the kitchen with damp hands trying to turn the toaster on.  Do not touch the knobs with damp hands...you will get a jolt so hard that it feels like a punch to your back.  This happened 2x in one week.  Learned my lesson. I just don\'t use this after washing dishes...or cutting anything damp.'),
