(7395, 11, 1, 1, '2014-04-12', 'Junk I can\'t believe that Black &Decker would sell a piece of junk like this item. It will not toast even and you have to watch it or it will burn. It also smokes. Stay away.'),
(7396, 5, 1, 1, '2015-04-18', 'A little overpriced even at this price ****teview update 5/8/14. Leaks all over counter now!!!! Takes about half an hour to brew! I still end up pouring water directly in rather than pulling out The reservoir because it\'s kind of a pain to do it. Its confusing to use at first due to the readout. Left coffee on all day and didn\'t even know was still on. Lastly, I would not say it brewed above average coffee in anyway shape or form. I even tried top-of-the-line grounds.'),
