(7408, 5, 1, 5, '2014-10-16', 'Great coffee pot! Great coffee pot.  The removable water reservoir is a great option, and the small wheels on the bottom make it very easy to pivot the machine to access the reservoir.  The wheels are angled so the machine goes in a circle and can\'t just roll of the counter.'),
