(7416, 4, 1, 4, '2015-06-30', 'Great toaster oven with one problem, but awesome 3 year warranty covered it! I\'ve had this toaster oven for 2.5 years now and the heating element on the bottom started to bend.  I really like the layout of the knobs, the look of it, the ease of use, the quality of toasting and baking and the fact that there are no annoying noises that come from it.  I was about to purchase it again but realized it is still under the 3 year warranty.  Yay!  I read other reviews that the cost of shipping and handling is not worth it, but want to let California residents know that all of it is covered for them.  It says in the warranty booklet.  Cuisinart did not volunteer that information on the phone, but when I brought it to their attention, they covered everything.  Getting a new toaster in 7-10 days.  :)  Hopefully the defective elements have been remedied by this time.'),
