(7420, 9, 1, 2, '2016-01-16', 'I really really wanted to love this machine I really really wanted to love this machine, but I don\'t.  I\'ve had it now for about a month and a half.  For the first week or so, it was great.  I would program it and have a really good cup of coffee every morning.  But then the coffee started tasting watered down.  At first I thought it was the coffee, so I tried a couple other brands.  Wasn\'t the coffee.  I tweaked the water to coffee ratio and still no good.  So i\'m at a loss and sending it back.'),
(7421, 3, 1, 4, '2015-12-31', 'Easy to use and clean Was really impressed with the quality. Heavy duty. Easy to use and clean. Exterior gets very hot so have to be careful.'),
(7422, 2, 1, 2, '2015-03-19', '1 out of the 4 feet was and inch shorter than the rest. I got a used one b/c description said the product was untouched, it was just the packaging that would be damaged.  Fine with me, $27 is a fairly good price for this model. However, upon arrival, the packaging was fine. The oven looked fine. I set it on my counter top to see that one of the 3 feet it rests on, is 1\" shorter than the rest. It wobbles. A lot. I jimmied something underneath it to steady it but I was bummed.'),
(7423, 9, 1, 2, '2016-07-23', 'Reservoir leaks a heavy stream I have only had this since April and now the reservoir leaks a heavy stream when refilled. I left a trail of water across my kitchen floor and my house slippers were soaked. After looking at the parts list I find there is no reservoir listed. I do not recommend this product ot anyone!'),
