(7425, 1, 1, 5, '2016-09-02', 'Perfect! We had a bigger keurig that was broken ... Perfect! We had a bigger keurig that was broken when we moved. We figured we didn\'t use that one as much anyway so we wanted something more compact. This keurig is simple to use, doesn\'t take a lot of space and is modern.'),
(7426, 6, 1, 2, '2016-12-21', 'Not toasting evenly I had high hopes for this toaster because of so many good reviews. However, after testing with three different types of bread, I found that the toaster is very poor at executing its primary function - toasting sliced bread evenly. Each side of a slice of bread was evenly toasted but the bread was toasted to very different levels on opposite sides. One side was very dark, almost burnt, and the opposite side was toasted too lightly. I was able to see that the heating elements were not heating evenly.'),
