(7430, 3, 1, 5, '2014-07-17', 'I love this convection oven I love this convection oven. I want a toaster in addition t something that would require me to use my oven less often. This is perfect. I\'ve made a pizza, broiled steaks and potatoes, and baked cookies in it so far. It works like a dream and it\'s very simple to use.'),
